ons League]]\n  | cup4 result        = '''Group Stage'''\n  | league topscorer   = <br />'''[[Predrag \u0110or\u0111evi\u0107]]''' (15)\n  | season topscorer   = <br />'''[[Predrag \u0110or\u0111evi\u0107]]''' (18)\n  | highest attendance = 33,500 vs [[Olympique Lyonnais]] (1 November 2005)\n|pattern_la1=_olympiacosfc0506h |pattern_b1=_olympiacosfc0506h |pattern_ra1=_olympiacosfc0506h |pattern_sh1=_olympiacosfc0506h |pattern_so1=_olympiacosfc0506h |leftarm1=F20D2F |body1=F20D2F |rightarm1=F20D2F |shorts1=F20D2F |socks1=F20D2F\n|pattern_la2= |pattern_b2=_olympiacosfc0506a |pattern_so2=_olympiacosfc0506a |pattern_ra2= |leftarm2=000000 |body2=C0C0C0 |rightarm2=000000 |shorts2=000000 |socks2=000000\n|pattern_la3= |pattern_b3=_olympiacosfc0506t |pattern_ra3= |pattern_sh3=_olympiacosfc0506t |pattern_so3=_olympiacosfc0506t |leftarm3=FFFFFF |body3=FFFFFF |rightarm3=FFFFFF |shorts3=FFFFFF |socks3=FFFFFF\n  | prevseason = [[2004\u201305 Olympiacos F.C. season|2004\u201305]]\n  | nextseason = [[2006\u201307 Olympiacos F.C. season|2006\u201307]]\n}}\nThe '''2005\u201306 season''' is '''[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]''' 47th consecutive season in the [[Super League Greece|Alpha Ethniki]] and their 9th consecutive season in the [[UEFA Champions League]]. In the beginning of the summertime Olympiacos named [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[Trond Sollied]] coach.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=314657.html |title=Sollied takes Olympiacos hot seat |publisher=[[UEFA|UEFA.com]] |date=2005-07-05 |accessdate=2008-05-29}}</ref>\n\n==Squad==\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=1|nat=Greece|name=[[Pantelis Kafes]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=2|nat=Greece|name=[[Christos Patsatzoglou]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=3|nat=Greece|name=[[Stelios Venetidis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=4|nat=Greece|name=[[Efthimios Kouloucheris]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=5|nat=Greece|name=[[Michalis Kapsis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=6|nat=Greece|name=[[Ieroklis Stoltidis]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|n